description: This repository contains the code and data for my thesis titled "Predicting Tennis Match Outcome: A Machine Learning Approach Using the SRP-CRISP-DM Framework." The project explores various machine learning techniques to predict the outcome of tennis matches, leveraging the SRP-CRISP-DM methodology for structured and effective data analysis.
